{{Infobox language |name=Adu |altname= |states=[[China]] |ethnicity=[[Yi people|Yi]] |speakers= |date= |ref= |familycolor=Sino-Tibetan |fam2=[[Lolo-Burmese languages|Lolo-Burmese]] |fam3=[[Loloish languages|Loloish]] |fam4=[[Nisoish languages|Nisoish]] |fam5=[[Southeastern Loloish|Southeastern]]?<ref name="Pelkey2011"/> |fam6=(unclassified) |iso3= |glotto= |glottorefname= }} '''Adu''' ({{zh|阿笃}}) is an unclassified [[Loloish languages|Loloish]] language of [[Huaning County]], [[Yunnan]], China.
Pelkey (2011:431)<ref name="Pelkey2011">Pelkey, Jamin. 2011. ''Dialectology As Dialectic: Interpreting Phula Variation''. Berlin: De Gruyter Mouton.</ref> suggests that the neighboring [[Xiqi language|Xiqi]], [[Ati language (China)|Ati]], and [[Long language|Long]] languages of [[Huaning County]] may be [[Southeastern Loloish languages]].
==Distribution== The ''Huaning County Gazetteer'' 华宁县志 (1994:514) lists the following locations of Adu. *Qinglong Town 青龙镇: Songzichang 松子场,<ref name="ynszxc">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249289|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇斗居村民委员会松子厂村|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref> Xinzhai 新寨,<ref name="ynszxc2">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249288|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇斗居村民委员会新寨村|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref> Douju 斗居,<ref name="ynszxc3">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249009|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇斗居村民委员会|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref> Chengmendong 城门洞,<ref name="ynszxc4">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249291|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇城门硐村民委员会城门硐村|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref> Niuqiduo 牛期多<ref name="ynszxc5">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249290|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇城门硐村民委员会牛期多村|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref> *Lufeng Township 禄丰乡: Gele 革勒<ref name="ynszxc6">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249021|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=华宁县青龙镇革勒村民委员会|accessdate=2017-12-30}}</ref>
