The '''Poko''' are a people of [[Transvaal Province |Transvaal]], [[South Africa]]. They were conquered in 1864 by the Boer settlers and [[Mswati II]].<ref name="Yakan1999">{{cite book|last=Yakan|first=Muḥammad Zuhdī|title=Almanac of African Peoples & Nations|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=B4VgTJaVqCwC&pg=PA601|accessdate=16 March 2012|year=1999|publisher=Transaction Publishers|isbn=978-1-56000-433-2|page=601}}</ref>

